&lt;p&gt;Beyond the basic palette of services related to the processing technologies of biomass pellet fuel DORAN GROUP also provides support and cooperation in the implementation of projects related to the combustion of biomass.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We cooperate with the best specialists from the energy and heating industry in the country as well as Europe, who had taken part in projects related with constructing of heat and power plant fueled with both: processed and unprocessed biomass(briquettes, pellets).&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Therefore, in our offer you will also find services related to:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;Consultancy on projects related with investments on the construction of boilers, heating plants and power plants for all types of biomass,&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;Designing biomass heating systems,&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;Modernization of existing boilers, heating plants in order to adapt them for supplying with power from biomass.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
